---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
---

<Layout title="idk.fm">
	<main>
		<p class="intro">Like any seasoned software engineer, my common sense dictates that some form of a portfolio website is necessary to demonstrate my experience, while a humble dose of imposter syndrome forever ensures that I don't go over the top.</p>
		<ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
			<Card
				href="https://github.com/agbfm"
				title="GitHub"
				body="Although most work happens behind closed doors, I'm building things in the open as much as possible."
			/>
			<Card
				href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/agbfm/"
				title="LinkedIn"
				body="My career experience described in a professional manner, complete with handsome wedding headshot."
			/>
		</ul>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1rem;
		width: 800px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
		color: white;
		font-size: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}
	.intro {
		padding: 2rem 0;
	}
	.link-card-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(24ch, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		padding: 0;
	}
</style>
